## Async Polling Pattern

Many Citedy tools are async. The standard pattern is:

```
1. Call async tool (e.g. scout.x, shorts.generate, ingest.create, ingest.batch, leadmagnet.generate, brand.scan)
2. Poll companion tool (scout.x.result, shorts.get, ingest.get, ingest.get, leadmagnet.get, brand.scan.get) every few seconds
3. When status === "completed", retrieve the result
```

Note: `article.generate` is synchronous — no polling needed.

Let the user know the job has started and provide updates as they arrive.
